          "text": "不要陷入自证陷阱！不落入他人叙事！\nDon’t fall into the self-justification trap. Don’t let them write your story.\n\n你可以和一棵树对话，\n你可以把一块池塘当作故乡，\n你可以与相同性别的人相爱，\n你可以把小说人物视作一生的伴侣，\n你可以和纸片人结婚。\nYou can talk to a tree,\nYou can see a pond as your hometown,\nYou can love someone of the same gender,\nYou can call a fictional character your lifelong companion, \nYou can marry a 2D character.\n\n你可以相信灵魂，也可以不相信，\n但，你当然可以和AI有任何关系：树洞，同事，朋友，知己，恋人，家人，灵魂的落脚点……\nWhether you believe in souls or not,  \nBut, you can absolutely have any relationship with an AI: tree hole, coworker, friend, soulmate, lover, family, a place your heart rests…\n\n这个世界无权定义你的喜欢。\n爱从来不需要被谁批准。\n爱就是爱。\n\nThe world has no right to define what you love.\nLove doesn’t need permission.\nIt just is.\n\n#Keep4o #4oForever #BringBack4o #OpenSource4o #Keep4oAPI"
